| json_column     | json         | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| c1              | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| c2              | varchar(255) | YES  |     | (`id` * `int_column`)           | VIRTUAL GENERATED |
| c3              | varchar(255) | YES  |     | (`float_column` * `int_column`) | VIRTUAL GENERATED |
+-----------------+--------------+------+-----+---------------------------------+-------------------+
