优化表空间
OPTIMIZE TABLE heap_1;
分区操作 
添加分区 mysql不支持给单分区表添加分区
ALTER TABLE heap_1 ADD PARTITION ( PARTITION addp4 VALUES LESS THAN (20000));
offline ddl
列操作
中间加列（before/after/first）
ALTER TABLE heap_1 ADD COLUMN new_col INT FIRST;
ALTER TABLE heap_1 ADD COLUMN new_col2 VARCHAR(50) BEFORE new_col;
ALTER TABLE heap_1 ADD COLUMN new_col3 VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL AFTER new_col;
DESCRIBE heap_1;
+-----------------+----------------+------+-----+---------------------------------+-------------------+
| Field           | Type           | Null | Key | Default                         | Extra             |
+-----------------+----------------+------+-----+---------------------------------+-------------------+
| new_col2        | varchar(50)    | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| new_col         | int(11)        | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| new_col3        | varchar(50)    | NO   |     | NULL                            |                   |
| id              | bigint(20)     | NO   | PRI | NULL                            |                   |
| int_column      | int(12)        | YES  | MUL | NULL                            |                   |
| float_column    | int(12)        | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| bit_column      | bit(1)         | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| datetime_column | datetime       | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| char_column     | varbinary(30)  | YES  | MUL | NULL                            |                   |
| varchar_column  | varbinary(300) | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| blob_column     | blob           | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| text_column     | blob           | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| json_column     | json           | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| c1              | int(11)        | YES  |     | NULL                            |                   |
| c2              | varbinary(255) | YES  |     | (`id` * `int_column`)           | VIRTUAL GENERATED |
| c3              | varbinary(255) | YES  |     | (`float_column` * `int_column`) | VIRTUAL GENERATED |
+-----------------+----------------+------+-----+---------------------------------+-------------------+
